# Post-Edit Verification

After making code edits, suggest the user run both checks before considering the work done:

```bash
npm run lint        # next lint
npm run typecheck   # tsc --noEmit
```

- Surface this suggestion once per batch of related edits, not after every single file.
- If you can run them yourself non-destructively, prefer running them and reporting results over just suggesting.
- Don't suggest these for non-code changes (docs, markdown, config-only tweaks that can't affect lint/types).
